# Cloud Storage hackathon data and generated runtime state
#
# Everything below is produced by running the agent, not by writing it. It also
# carries session content -- the audit trail, refusal flags, and member feedback
# -- so it must never be pushed, least of all to a Humana-connected remote.
# The synthetic CSVs under data/runtime/extracted/ ARE tracked on purpose: they
# are the fixture the tests and the demo run against.
caregap_compass/data/runtime/audit.jsonl
caregap_compass/data/runtime/compliance_flags.jsonl
caregap_compass/data/runtime/feedback.db
caregap_compass/data/runtime/sessions.db
caregap_compass/data/runtime/raw/
caregap_compass/runtime/
*.db
*.jsonl
!caregap_compass/data/runtime/reference/*.jsonl

